definition.en: Net financial account (assets minus liabilities, transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).
Financial account assets (transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).
Financial account liabilities (transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).
Net financial account, direct investment (assets minus liabilities, transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).
Financial account, direct investment assets (transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).
Financial account, direct investment liabilities (transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).
Net financial account, portfolio investment (assets minus liabilities, transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).
Financial account, portfolio investment assets (transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).
Financial account, portfolio investment liabilities (transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).
Net financial account, other investment (assets minus liabilities, transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).
Financial account, other investment assets (transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).
Financial account, other investment liabilities (transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).

Net financial account as percentage of gross domestic product (GDP) at market prices (assets minus liabilities, transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 and ESA 2010 standards).

Financial account assets as percentage of gross domestic product (GDP) at market prices (assets, transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards and ESA 2010 standards).

Financial account liabilities as percentage of gross domestic product (GDP) at market prices (liabilities, transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards and ESA 2010 standards).
